        "subject": "LU-8972 osp: delete orphans when precreate failed",
        "message": "LU-8972 osp: delete orphans when precreate failed\n\nWhen OSP precreates objects on OST, the objects could already be\ncreated on OST even if the precreate request fails, these objects\nshould be deleted when OSP restores connection to OST.\n\nChange-Id: Id9432e18e9bd5820c7ed4f90d466b8eb3a5a5267\nSigned-off-by: Hongchao Zhang <hongchao.zhang@intel.com>\n"
